{"id":83435,"title":"One Health and emergency preparedness.","abstract":"Emergencies such as hurricanes, floods and nuclear disasters do not just affect people and the environment; they also affect domestic animals. In this latest article in Veterinary Record's One Health series, Kendra Stauffer and Lisa Conti discuss how One Health considerations are being incorporated into emergency preparedness planning in the USA.","date":"2014-10-31","categories":"Pathological Conditions and Signs and Symptoms","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25359746","annotations":[{"name":"Environment (biophysical)","weight":0.797998,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Environment_(biophysical)"},{"name":"Natural environment","weight":0.761555,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Natural_environment"},{"name":"Flood","weight":0.750806,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flood"},{"name":"Tropical cyclone","weight":0.746519,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tropical_cyclone"},{"name":"Disaster","weight":0.685027,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disaster"},{"name":"Emergency management","weight":0.659933,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emergency_management"},{"name":"Emergency","weight":0.580921,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emergency"},{"name":"Health","weight":0.551527,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health"},{"name":"Nuclear weapon","weight":0.472639,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nuclear_weapon"},{"name":"Nuclear and radiation accidents","weight":0.394347,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nuclear_and_radiation_accidents"},{"name":"Planning","weight":0.366738,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Planning"},{"name":"United States","weight":0.352436,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_States"},{"name":"Veterinary medicine","weight":0.248919,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.w